Generators are available with specifications including wattage ranging from 5 kW to 20 kW, current at 480 V ranging from 10 A to 40 A, power ranging from 13.9 hp to 35 hp at 1800 rpm, & fuel consumption ranging from 0.465 gph to 1.98 gph.
